Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who'll succeed L will be Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, Near will handle things calmly and objectively, like he's solving a puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving...
