Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Mason, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's just say he is L's true successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.24,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,78)\fad(650,450)}The United States of America...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:32.33,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,SPK = Secret Provision for Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:32.33,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(177,145)\fad(650,450)}established the SPK, \Na brand-new counter-Kira organization \Nwith no links to L,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:38.75,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(168,110)\fad(650,450)}comprised of selected agents from the FBI and CIA, in addition to Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.76,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,339)}Abduction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, under the present circumstances, controlling information on the Internet is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the investigation into Kira has been at a standstill for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who post the names of the people they want dead on the Internet are the ones I really want them to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because Kira requires information from the Internet, there's no way they'd kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely contradicting yourself, Matsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, certainly, the conclusion that as long as you don't do anything bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that for law-abiding people in general, the world has changed for the better, {\alpha&HFF&}will be an easy conclusion for some people to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that for law-abiding people in general, the world has changed for the better, will be an easy conclusion for some people to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fine one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, soon everyone will see it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all talking about that again? Give it a rest, darling. Same with you Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, Misa-san, it's a surprise to see you two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse our intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Matsuda-san", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm indebted to you for always taking care of my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Sayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've really grown up... umm, you've become even more beautiful... erm, the last time I saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu's face has gone bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I didn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let Sayu marry a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. There's no way I would allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! No way... I haven't even asked her out, let alone proposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fath--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I think Matsuda-san is lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really, Sayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and if you were maybe ten years younger, I might even have considered dating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've learned to handle yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she seems so much more mature than Matsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed at all. You've always been this wonderful from the moment I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you've got a job too now. Don't just live together, hurry up and get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a unfortunate family playing "happy families"... {\alpha&HFF&}this is too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a unfortunate family playing "happy families"... this is too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, Light. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abduction? {\alpha&HFF&}Who's abducted who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abduction? Who's abducted who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief of the Police Force, Takimura... {\alpha&HFF&}We have no idea who the culprit is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief of the Police Force, Takimura... We have no idea who the culprit is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why now, when the Kira investigation is in this state...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received the call at 6:12 pm; around 45 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've traced the call back to the Chief's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the culprit made any demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... {\alpha&HFF&}they'll exchange the Chief... for the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... they'll exchange the Chief... {\alpha&HFF&}for the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... they'll exchange the Chief... for the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this and why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily. If people found out about the notebook there would be countless people who would want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, how much does the Chief know about the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information regarding the notebook was supposed to be kept to the people in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I swear I haven't told the Chief anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the existence of the Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}and that the police have it... and they're coming after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the existence of the Death Note, and that the police have it... {\alpha&HFF&}and they're coming after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the existence of the Death Note, and that the police have it... and they're coming after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notify all police departments of the abduction only.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the culprits made contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's someone here to see Takimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm FBI agent John McEnroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my real name of course, but I'm here regarding Kira, so please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... I'm afraid the Chief isn't available right now, but you can discuss the matter with me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get straight to the point... the Japanese police force can't be depended on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to solve the Kira case, we'd like you to hand the notebook over to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was the FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you hidden the Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act as if you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize this is a serious crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing to gain by abducting the Chief of the Japanese police force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how did you find out about the notebook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that someone has abducted the Chief of the police force, {\alpha&HFF&}and their aim seems to be to obtain the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that someone has abducted the Chief of the police force, and their aim seems to be to obtain the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, steer the conversation toward assisting them with the rescue of the Chief and apprehending the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we get the chance, we'll seize the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me? This is HQ... here are your orders:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Japanese police backed out of the Kira investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:11:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in reality, the only ones working on the case with L were Yagami Souichirou, Mogi Kanzou and Matsuda Touta. {\alpha&HFF&}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in reality, the only ones working on the case with L were Yagami Souichirou, Mogi Kanzou and Matsuda Touta. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was another man called Ukita, but he was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that explains why the Chief of the Police Force didn't even know of the notebook's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese police are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all them, the one with the highest rank was Yagami, the guy in command of headquarters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, there should be two notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has one, and the Japanese police has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we do as Mello says, nothing will go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the year and a half Mello's been here, has he been wrong about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would someone like you, who joined us by bringing the head of a mafia boss that even Kira hadn't managed to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be so hung up over a notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't just want the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill anyone who gets in my way, {\alpha&HFF&}and become number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill anyone who gets in my way, and become number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes to beat Near to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry... Eddie and I were kinda dozing off and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takimura has managed to kill himself using his necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! This won't work without a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is Kira's work, it means they don't know our names or faces, so they killed Takimura instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, Kira is someone who knows about this abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, we'll abduct Yagami Souichirou's daughter, Yagami Sayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no clues regarding the whereabouts of the Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits haven't made further contact since abducting him. What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. {\alpha&HFF&}That FBI agent called himself "John McEnroe"... His real name is Rally Connors, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. That FBI agent called himself "John McEnroe"... {\alpha&HFF&}His real name is Rally Connors, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light. That FBI agent called himself "John McEnroe"... His real name is Rally Connors, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? {\alpha&HFF&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation is real too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head of the FBI himself offered his assistance in rescuing the Chief... {\alpha&HFF&}I guess we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head of the FBI himself offered his assistance in rescuing the Chief... I guess we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief should already be dead... {\alpha&HFF&}why haven't they said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief should already be dead... why haven't they said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead, so they're just giving up the exchange? {\alpha&HFF&}Is that the kind of opponent they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead, so they're just giving up the exchange? Is that the kind of opponent they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... no, everyone else that's here too. You all need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Chief doesn't know about the notebook, he knows who was investigating alongside L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he reveals that, there is a chance that they'll come after us--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to bed by myself tonight, like a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here aren't the only ones in danger! {\alpha&HFF&}Our families and--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here aren't the only ones in danger! Our families and--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief's cell phone number... it's from the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trace the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief... {\alpha&HFF&}about the deal regarding the exchange of the Chief for the notebook... that's now off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief... about the deal regarding the exchange of the Chief for the notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}that's now off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief... about the deal regarding the exchange of the Chief for the notebook... that's now off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takimura is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y-{\alpha&HFF&}You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal is only off as far as the Chief is concerned. {\alpha&HFF&}Instead, we'll now exchange the notebook in return for Yagami Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal is only off as far as the Chief is concerned. Instead, we'll now exchange the notebook in return for Yagami Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Deputy Chief of the Police, we know it's pointless to tell you not to contact the police, but we would like you to act alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we see any big movements by the police, we'll kill your daughter, without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we did with the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending you images of Takimura's corpse. Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-{\alpha&HFF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me! {\alpha&HFF&}They've manipulated Takimura's death to their own advantage, and now Sayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me! They've manipulated Takimura's death to their own advantage, and now Sayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, things are getting interesting again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they have to go this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling? Isn't this rather unusual of you? Calling from your work cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, she's pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I figure it, the kidnappers didn't kill the Chief; Kira did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably did that to prevent the kidnappers from acquiring the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira prefers to think of themselves as just, so they wouldn't want the notebook falling into evil hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira did kill the Chief, then we've got to assume that they have some way of accessing police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off if we act by using only the people here. {\alpha&HFF&}If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off if we act by using only the people here. If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira may try and kill the hostage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, the abducted Chief of the Japanese police has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom? {\alpha&HFF&}By the people that abducted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom? By the people that abducted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be interesting if it turns out that Kira was the one who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. If the hostage dies, then they'd be unable to exchange him for the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}it narrows the list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it was Kira, it narrows the list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Commander Lester, any news on his whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}it's certain that four years ago he was at the orphanage you mentioned... after that, we have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's certain that four years ago he was at the orphanage you mentioned... {\alpha&HFF&}after that, we have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's certain that four years ago he was at the orphanage you mentioned... after that, we have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, you always get too emotional and neglect what's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you really have nothing to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange that you'd leave a photo of yourself behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter has finally arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have an idea as to where we are by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the exchange here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. {\alpha&HFF&}With the notebook. Within two days. In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. With the notebook. {\alpha&HFF&}Within two days. In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. With the notebook. Within two days. {\alpha&HFF&}In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone. With the notebook. Within two days. In LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no exchange unless you guarantee that my daughter is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it. I'll mail you a picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief! We've narrowed it down to Los Angeles' Fifth Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The TV program pictured in the background is currently airing in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken it on purpose to let us know she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}Thank god... at least we know she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank god... {\alpha&HFF&}at least we know she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank god... at least we know she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the notebook to LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going as the Deputy Chief of the Police Force, and also as Yagami Sayu's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make all the decisions and accept full responsibility for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Wait until we've worked out a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Deputy Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got to get to LA within two days. There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that the kidnappers didn't kill Takimura; Kira did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just mentioning it as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, Kira somehow managed to obtain information from the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's L... {\alpha&HFF&}the current one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's L... the current one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard what John McEnroe, {\alpha&HFF&}or Agent Rally Connors, had to say from Deputy Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard what John McEnroe, or Agent Rally Connors, {\alpha&HFF&}had to say from Deputy Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard what John McEnroe, or Agent Rally Connors, had to say from Deputy Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you assist us in the investigation into the murder of Chief Takimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second-generation L... {\alpha&HFF&}it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second-generation L... it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Second-generation"? {\alpha&HFF&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Second-generation"? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a newly established organization especially created to investigate Kira independently of L, called the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven main members of this organization all know about L's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's death? {\alpha&HFF&}Who and where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's death? Who and where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am the one at the center of the SPK...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm N.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... I'm N.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"N"? {\alpha&HFF&}Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"N"? Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... {\alpha&HFF&}this feeling... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... this feeling... {\alpha&HFF&}what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... this feeling... what is it?
